  "title": "Preschool Educators",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a passionate <strong>Preschool Educator</strong> to create a nurturing and engaging environment for young children. If you love working with children and believe in fostering their holistic development, join our team!</p><p><br /></p><p>Locations: Ang Mo Kio</p><h3><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></h3><ul><li>Plan and implement age-appropriate teaching, learning, and caregiving approaches.</li><li>Observe and document children’s learning progress.</li><li>Ensure a safe, healthy, and stimulating environment.</li><li>Build strong relationships with children, families, and the community.</li><li>Support accreditation and licensing processes.</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements:</strong></h3><ul><li>Advanced Certificate in Early Years (ACEY), Certificate in Early Childhood Care & Education (ECCE), or Diploma in ECCE.</li><li>At least 2 years of experience working with young children.</li><li>Knowledge of early childhood development theories and best practices.</li><li>Strong teamwork and communication skills.</li></ul><p>📩 <strong>Apply now</strong> and be part of a team that nurtures the future generation!</p>",
